<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَالَ الْأَزْدِيّ كَذَّاب<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٧٤٢ - حباب بن فضَالة الذهلي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
